|               |         Projection: v1.i_category, v1.i_brand, v1.s_store_name, v1.s_company_name, v1.d_year, v1.sum_sales, v1.avg_monthly_sales, v1.rn, v1_lag.sum_sales                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
